<i>the first person to come forward</i>

53:54.064 --> 53:57.234
<i>with allegations of abuse</i>
<i>against Father Maskell?"</i>

53:59.695 --> 54:02.065
The archdiocese's answer: "Yes.

54:02.156 --> 54:06.236
Archdiocesan files do not reflect any
kind of abuse allegation against Maskell

54:06.326 --> 54:09.326
before Jane Doe came forward in 1992."

54:12.207 --> 54:13.127
[Charles] <i>That's a shame.</i>

54:13.709 --> 54:14.539
That's a shame.

54:14.960 --> 54:16.000
[man] Question number two.

54:17.421 --> 54:22.091
<i>"How and when did the Archdiocese</i>
<i>first hear allegations of abuse</i>

54:22.176 --> 54:23.796
<i>against Father Maskell?"</i>

54:24.678 --> 54:26.388
The archdiocese's answer:

54:27.097 --> 54:28.967
"See answer to number one."

54:29.892 --> 54:30.772
Hmm.

54:33.228 --> 54:34.058
They're lying.

54:35.272 --> 54:36.192
They're lying.

54:36.273 --> 54:38.573
Of course there was allegations.

54:40.068 --> 54:41.318
[man] Question number three.

54:42.070 --> 54:48.080
<i>"Were any disciplinary interventions made</i>
<i>against Father Maskell prior to 1992?"</i>

54:51.079 --> 54:53.079
The archdiocese's answer: "No."

54:53.999 --> 54:55.329
That's it, just "no"?

54:58.754 --> 55:00.134
<i>This is disgusting.</i>

55:01.632 --> 55:02.842
This is disgusting.

55:05.302 --> 55:08.142
He's saying nothing happened before me,

55:08.847 --> 55:10.347
so-- And Charles is saying,

55:10.432 --> 55:12.062
<i>"Oh, no, definitely, it did."</i>

55:14.353 --> 55:18.573
If you start saying things like,
"That never happened."

55:20.192 --> 55:22.532
What you're calling me is a liar.

55:25.405 --> 55:27.615
<i>How about the meeting with Malooly?</i>

55:28.784 --> 55:29.954
<i>What did that concern?</i>

55:33.664 --> 55:35.124
I'd love to hear the answer.

55:37.626 --> 55:41.126
<i>They knew my mother contacted</i>
<i>the Archdiocese of Baltimore.</i>

55:42.047 --> 55:45.427
<i>They knew why Maskell</i>
<i>was asked to leave St. Clement's</i>

55:45.509 --> 55:49.009
<i>in May of '67 and put at Keough.</i>

55:49.721 --> 55:50.601
<i>They knew that.</i>

55:53.850 --> 55:57.900
I guess that, you know, buddy,
there are lies and there are lies, okay?

55:58.522 --> 56:00.232
You wanna deal with that bullshit,

56:00.983 --> 56:03.943
you might be able to get away with it,
okay?

56:04.027 --> 56:04.947
And that's a lie.

56:06.280 --> 56:07.110
[Jean] Man.

56:08.991 --> 56:10.121
I'm telling you...

56:11.535 --> 56:15.455
and especially right after I finished up
this damn mediation

56:15.914 --> 56:19.634
and they pick and pull
with every little tiny penny--

56:19.710 --> 56:21.840
And they act like what you went through,

56:21.920 --> 56:25.010
they care about,
and they could give two shits, really.

56:25.799 --> 56:27.509
And some part of this

56:27.593 --> 56:32.313
is really squelching people's anger,

56:32.389 --> 56:34.849
and people's righteous anger,

56:34.933 --> 56:38.523
and people's need for you
to make things public

56:38.604 --> 56:40.404
and stop acting like it's--

56:43.817 --> 56:46.357
That-- That we're invisible.
We're not invisible.

57:25.275 --> 57:26.395
[Abbie] Okay, here's the letter.

57:27.235 --> 57:29.355
"Dear Seton Keough Alumnae and Friends,

57:29.696 --> 57:32.946
it is with a heavy heart that I sit
and write this November message.

57:33.533 --> 57:37.623
As I am sure you have heard, Seton Keough
will be closing its doors in June."

57:40.374 --> 57:42.424
<i>Many Keough graduates</i>

57:42.501 --> 57:45.711
<i>are glad to see the circle closed,</i>
<i>the doors shut.</i>

57:47.130 --> 57:49.090
<i>This piece of history destroyed.</i>

57:53.720 --> 57:58.230
<i>I wasn't particularly a conspiracy</i>
<i>theorist, as I think of it, at first.</i>

57:58.308 --> 58:00.438
<i>I was just interested in who hurt Cathy.</i>

58:01.478 --> 58:06.818
<i>But the abuse angle of this just took off</i>
<i>running and grew and grew and grew.</i>

58:08.318 --> 58:10.818
<i>I share the pain of my classmates,</i>

58:10.904 --> 58:13.784
<i>who lived through some horrendous years.</i>

58:16.618 --> 58:18.748
At night when I can't sleep and I--

58:18.829 --> 58:22.499
I say, "If I think about this a little
harder, I can figure this out,"

58:22.582 --> 58:23.672
um, at 3 a.m.

58:25.460 --> 58:26.840
<i>It seems like</i>

58:27.587 --> 58:32.377
<i>even when I try to look at her murder</i>
<i>as the work of a random lone wolf,</i>

58:33.051 --> 58:35.351
<i>the abuse issues always come back in.</i>

58:48.066 --> 58:49.436
How are you?

58:49.985 --> 58:51.895
-I'm so happy to see you.
-[chuckling]

58:52.487 --> 58:56.407
[Gemma] <i>Jane Doe was led to believe</i>
<i>that she was the only one.</i>

58:57.659 --> 59:01.289
If Maskell had been nailed

59:01.705 --> 59:05.285
the first time the abuse was reported,

59:05.834 --> 59:10.844
then how do we even know
how many people could have been saved?

59:11.423 --> 59:14.263
<i>I personally know of 35 names</i>

59:14.509 --> 59:17.549
<i>of abuse victims of Joseph Maskell.</i>

59:17.929 --> 59:20.019
<i>Some aren't even living anymore.</i>

59:20.390 --> 59:24.690
<i>There were suicides,</i>
<i>alcoholism, drug addiction.</i>

59:28.023 --> 59:31.693
<i>And what happened to them set their fate.</i>

59:33.862 --> 59:35.032
<i>If somebody...</i>

59:36.198 --> 59:37.488
<i>had listened...</i>

59:39.367 --> 59:42.577
<i>how many other lives could've been saved?</i>

59:49.461 --> 59:50.921
<i>Cathy would be here.</i>

59:55.675 --> 59:57.385
She would still be here.

01:00:08.021 --> 01:00:10.481
[Marilyn] "<i>Some people meet death</i>
<i>With open arms</i>

01:00:11.608 --> 01:00:13.778
<i>And thank God their time has come</i>

01:00:14.694 --> 01:00:17.534
<i>Others beg to be spared</i>
<i>For just one more day</i>

01:00:18.365 --> 01:00:20.275
<i>Saying there's much to be done</i>

01:00:22.661 --> 01:00:26.711
<i>But if we, before performing an act</i>
<i>Would stop and think of death</i>

01:00:28.708 --> 01:00:33.668
<i>Of death, of judgment</i>
<i>And of all such things</i>

01:00:35.423 --> 01:00:37.513
<i>I'm sure we would do our best</i>

01:00:39.636 --> 01:00:43.306
<i>So that when our time comes, we may say:</i>

01:00:45.183 --> 01:00:47.393
<i>'Take me, Lord, without delay'"</i>

01:00:51.064 --> 01:00:52.024
She was 16...

01:00:53.191 --> 01:00:54.481
<i>when she wrote that poem.</i>

01:00:57.529 --> 01:00:58.989
<i>Cathy's life,</i>

01:00:59.573 --> 01:01:01.453
Cathy's death and this abuse...

01:01:02.826 --> 01:01:04.616
<i>this is all connected.</i>

01:01:07.956 --> 01:01:10.626
<i>These girls have lived</i>
<i>with this all of their life.</i>

01:01:11.459 --> 01:01:14.299
I've lived with the loss of-- Of--

01:01:15.130 --> 01:01:18.840
My best friend, my sister,
all my life and I will carry that.

01:01:19.217 --> 01:01:21.677
But they also have pain they are carrying.

01:01:23.096 --> 01:01:25.716
And there needs to be a world,

01:01:25.807 --> 01:01:28.057
there needs to be a place that we live in,

01:01:28.143 --> 01:01:31.063
where people wanna see something
done about that.

01:01:36.568 --> 01:01:40.028
[Abbie] <i>Whoever murdered her</i>
<i>has gotten away with it,</i>

01:01:41.448 --> 01:01:42.278
<i>and...</i>

01:01:44.367 --> 01:01:48.367
she's never gotten a bit of justice.

01:01:50.957 --> 01:01:53.837
[Gemma] <i>It has been almost 50 years,</i>

01:01:54.211 --> 01:01:56.131
<i>since Cathy's murder,</i>

01:01:57.214 --> 01:02:00.014
<i>but I do think it'll be solved.</i>

01:02:02.385 --> 01:02:03.505
I won't rest.

01:02:04.763 --> 01:02:05.763
Mm-mm.

01:02:10.810 --> 01:02:12.980
[Jean] <i>Can we find justice?</i>

01:02:14.689 --> 01:02:18.819
Can justice just be acknowledged
from the community

01:02:18.902 --> 01:02:21.912
instead of waiting
for the stamp of approval

01:02:22.280 --> 01:02:27.120
from the systems
that we usually get it from?

01:02:29.287 --> 01:02:31.367
[C.T.] <i>That's what the state</i>
<i>is supposed to be doing.</i>

01:02:32.082 --> 01:02:33.792
We can't have you be un-robbed...

01:02:34.876 --> 01:02:38.206
or un-raped or un-shot.

01:02:38.797 --> 01:02:40.377
<i>We can't un-ring those bells.</i>

01:02:41.424 --> 01:02:43.594
<i>What we can do is hold people accountable.</i>

01:02:58.608 --> 01:03:00.568
[Jean] <i>For many, many, many years,</i>

01:03:01.444 --> 01:03:02.864
<i>I didn't remember anything,</i>

01:03:03.446 --> 01:03:07.736
and one of the first things that I started
remembering was Cathy Cesnik.

01:03:10.120 --> 01:03:13.420
<i>This woman, she died</i>

01:03:13.498 --> 01:03:16.128
<i>to help stop what was going on</i>
<i>over there.</i>

01:03:18.336 --> 01:03:19.706
And because of the

01:03:19.796 --> 01:03:23.676
<i>Justice for Cathy group,</i>
<i>because of Cathy's sister,</i>

01:03:24.384 --> 01:03:28.184
<i>um, having the courage to come into this</i>

01:03:28.263 --> 01:03:32.603
to ask questions and to kind of
find her own peace,

01:03:34.019 --> 01:03:37.109
I'm finding another layer of that closure

01:03:37.522 --> 01:03:39.942
where I can say, "Okay."

01:03:42.652 --> 01:03:45.032
<i>You can't bury the truth so deep</i>
<i>it doesn't come up.</i>

01:03:54.748 --> 01:03:55.668
I'm ready.

01:04:03.423 --> 01:04:07.013
<i>If I could speak for myself</i>
<i>and maybe others,</i>

01:04:08.303 --> 01:04:09.933
<i>this is the opportunity.</i>

01:04:11.639 --> 01:04:13.219
It's like a little crack...

01:04:14.351 --> 01:04:18.191
and I personally feel that what I'm doing,

01:04:18.646 --> 01:04:21.896
facing my fear, is coming up to the crack
and saying,

01:04:21.983 --> 01:04:25.703
"Hello, do you know we're here?

01:04:26.112 --> 01:04:28.032
Is anyone out there?"

01:04:32.494 --> 01:04:34.124
And it's still silent.

01:04:35.413 --> 01:04:36.873
<i>But we're hearing each other...</i>

01:04:38.041 --> 01:04:40.171
<i>because we're all coming up to the crack.</i>

01:04:41.294 --> 01:04:43.254
<i>And what's happening is,</i>

01:04:43.338 --> 01:04:45.168
<i>is we're bumping into each other,</i>

01:04:45.715 --> 01:04:47.085
<i>coming to the crack.</i>

01:04:48.468 --> 01:04:52.008
And before you know it,
the pressure of that voice

01:04:53.139 --> 01:04:57.939
seeping through the crack
is going to shatter it.

